OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRain,
OL,6,Flocally heavy, spreading east
OL,7,FWednesday. Blustery showers following.
OL,8,FBreezy Thursday with sunny spells and
OL,9,Fscattered showers, heavy and thundery.
OL,10,FPerhaps drier Friday, but with further
OL,11,Fshowers likely. Staying cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
